OPEN TERMINAL TYPE IN ["  roslaunch turtlebot3_gazebo turtlebot3_world.launch  "] to launch the turtle bot on gazebo

open another terminal window type in [ nano ~/catkin_ws/src/avaa_nav/scripts/forward_5_seconds.py ] to check and edit the python file 

1.RUN [ cd ~/catkin_ws ] TO ENTER CATKIN TO RUN CODE SO THT ROBOT MOVES AUTONOMOUSLY
2.RUN [ source ~/catkin_ws/devel/setup.bash ] INSIDE CATKINS
3.RUN [ rosrun avaa_nav forward_5_seconds.py ] INSIDE CATKIN for it to run the code on ur bot on gazebo 
^^^ SHOULD work for autonomous movement on GAZEBO ^^^

**TO RUN IT ON GAZEBO WITH UR KEYBOARD (NOT AUTONOMOUS)**

1.LAUNCH ON GAZEBO [ roslaunch turtlebot3_teleop turtlebot3_teleop_key.launch ] usin ros launch and the "teleop" can control robot with keybaord
2.OPEN NEW TERMINAL AND RUN [ roslaunch turtlebot3_teleop turtlebot3_teleop_key.launch ] on this terminal u can control the robot via w,a,s,d

